txt.en: In the coming days, the Orcs will have to divert their resources to gathering more provisions.

Food is a valuable resource this high up in the mountains. The Orcs in Târ-kútoz keep their foul provisions stocked in containers scattered around the camp. Destroying them would force the Orcs to use resources to secure more food.
The Orc camp Târ-kútoz guards the watch-tower Atrad-zarakh.\n\nDestroying their provisions would force the Orcs to use resources to secure more food.
Food is a valuable resource this high up in the mountains, even for the Orcs.
